Liberty Brand Canning Company, a corporation of the State of Delaware, vs. American Stores Company, a corporation of the State of Delaware. (October 24, 1921.)

Pennewill, C. J., Heisel and Richards, J. J., sitting.

James M. Satterfield for plaintiff. Henry Ridgely and George M. Fisher, Jr., for defendant. Superior Court for Kent County,

October Term, 1921.

Foreign attachment, No. 17

October term, 1921.

*494Per Curiam.

It is ordered that the return of service in this case be vacated and set aside.
